### Root
GET http://localhost:5051/

### Get all users
GET http://localhost:5051/users

### Get user by ID (may crash)
GET http://localhost:5051/users/99

### Create user (no validation)
POST http://localhost:5051/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "email": "not-an-email"
}

### Update user (may crash)
PUT http://localhost:5051/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 999,
  "name": "",
  "email": ""
}

### Delete user (wrong route)
DELETE http://localhost:5051/users/1